rows.label: qst201913_0010
rows.name: There is nowhere left to run, feathered fool!

rows.label: qst201913_0020
rows.name: Repent and return that which does not belong to you!

rows.label: qst201913_0030
rows.name:
We not obliged to give back one coin!
You the fool for being tricked!

rows.label: qst201913_0040
rows.name: Why you... Infidel!

rows.label: qst201913_0050
rows.name: Just wait a minute, Rinne!

rows.label: qst201913_0060
rows.name: Divine Punishment!

rows.label: qst201913_0070
rows.name: Mo-mo-mooooo!

rows.label: qst201913_0080
rows.name: Ahh... In our fit of anger, we...

rows.label: qst201913_0090
rows.name: No! Our gold! Our precious 1,000,000 goooold!

rows.label: qst201913_0100
rows.name: The great unwashed are lining their pockets with it...

rows.label: qst201913_0110
rows.name: You've really done it now.

rows.label: qst201913_0120
rows.name: I tried to stop you...

rows.label: qst201913_0130
rows.name: Ahh... Ahhhh...

rows.label: qst201913_0140
rows.name: Hey, lady!

rows.label: qst201913_0150
rows.name: ...Hmm?

rows.label: qst201913_0160
rows.name: Here! This is yours, isn't it?

rows.label: qst201913_0170
rows.name: You... You would return this to us?

rows.label: qst201913_0180
rows.name: Yeah. Everyone needs money, don't they?

rows.label: qst201913_0190
rows.name: Oh, sweet, sweet child. Oh purest angel!

rows.label: qst201913_0200
rows.name: All of you... You do this for our sake...

rows.label: qst201913_0210
rows.name: You have...our sincerest thanks!

rows.label: qst201913_0220
rows.name: It is we who were the fools.

rows.label: qst201913_0230
rows.name:
To have doubted you even for a moment...
We are undeserving of such honesty.

rows.label: qst201913_0240
rows.name: ...Wait. You deserve a reward!

rows.label: qst201913_0250
rows.name: We shall invite you all to a magnificent tea party!

rows.label: qst201913_0260
rows.name: Really?!

rows.label: qst201913_0270
rows.name: Sounds amazing!

rows.label: qst201913_0280
rows.name: Huh?! You're gonna invite all these kids?!

rows.label: qst201913_0290
rows.name: That is correct. The money is no longer of any consequence.

rows.label: qst201913_0300
rows.name:
For we have found something more precious
than all the world's jewels.

rows.label: qst201913_0310
rows.name: These pure, perfectly innocent children have opened our eyes.

rows.label: qst201913_0320
rows.name:
We were wrong to focus solely on gathering an entourage
and holding magnificent parties.

rows.label: qst201913_0330
rows.name:
What we really should have been seeking was the
unblemished hearts of these darling children.

rows.label: qst201913_0340
rows.name:
Inviting these children to our tea party is more
than enough to make us happy.

rows.label: qst201913_0350
rows.name: Rinne...are you sure about this?

rows.label: qst201913_0360
rows.name: If there is one thing we are sure of, it's this.

rows.label: qst201913_0370
rows.name: Our dream remains, only redirected.

rows.label: qst201913_0380
rows.name:
Well then, maybe I just might decide to
tag along too!

rows.label: qst201913_0390
rows.name: Would you mind if I joined you as well?

rows.label: qst201913_0400
rows.name: Absolutely. The more the merrier!

rows.label: qst201913_0410
rows.name: Mmm, this is super tasty!

rows.label: qst201913_0420
rows.name: Hehehe! I've never had anything like this before!

rows.label: qst201913_0430
rows.name:
It gladdens us to hear that.
From the bottom of our heart!

rows.label: qst201913_0440
rows.name:
Do help yourselves to tea and treats.
It's all there for your delectation!

rows.label: qst201913_0450
rows.name: Let us have a celebration to end all others!

rows.label: qst201913_0460
rows.name:
So tell me... Why are we the ones serving
the food again?

rows.label: qst201913_0470
rows.name: This outrage! Tora not accept this!

rows.label: qst201913_0480
rows.name:
Shush, you! Just grin and bear it!
Don't go ruining the moment for them!

rows.label: qst201913_0490
rows.name: *sigh*
